The paper discusses the use of attention mechanisms in neural machine translation and image captioning, which are both subfields of natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and the use of multimodal data, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
